  <title translate="true">MODFLOW 6 Example: Activating MODPATH</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">MODFLOW 6 Example: Activating MODPATH</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Next we will activate MODPATH and use it to visualize flow in our model.</text></para>
    <list id="4" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Select "Model|MODFLOW Packages and Programs" and activate MODPATH. Be sure that MODPATH version 7 and Pathlilnes are both selected.</text><br /><image src="Modflow6ExampleModpath7Activation.bmp" scale="-99.90%" width="470" height="352" styleclass="Image Caption"><title translate="true">Activating MODPATH</title><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[Activating MODPATH]]></caption></image></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">On the Version 6 &amp; 7 options tab, set StopOption to Stop at termination points.</text><br /><image src="Modflow6ExampleModpath7StopOption.bmp" scale="-99.90%" width="470" height="352" styleclass="Image Caption"><title translate="true">StopOption</title><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[StopOption ]]></caption></image></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Click OK to close the dialog box.</text></li>
    </list>
  </body>
